Now, we sum these amounts step by step:

• 88,194.75 + 52,101.64 = 140,296.39  
• 140,296.39 + 52,410.28 = 192,706.67  
• 192,706.67 + 55,124.83 = 247,831.50  
• 247,831.50 + 52,927.55 = 300,759.05
